Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Have you ever said I wish I would have known that? Daily notes to the younger me is a collection of thoughts addressed to my younger self on things I wish I would have known at a younger age. From daily living tips to preparing for the future, Daily Notes to the Younger Me provides insights into what I should have done.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
